<h1>Notes from building software and running long</h1>

<section class="intro">
  <img
    class="profile-photo"
    src="/profile-photo.png"
    alt="Oleksandr Khomenko"
    width="160"
    height="160"
  />

  <p>
    I am Oleksandr Khomenko. I build software systems and write about the parts
    that make teams faster or slower in practice: architecture, AI-assisted
    development, developer infrastructure, review, ownership, and feedback.
  </p>

  <p>
    I also run long distances. That shows up here because training has changed
    how I think about pace, recovery, consistency, and how performance compounds.
  </p>

  <p>
    This site is where I keep the essays and notes I want to return to.
  </p>
</section>

<h2>Essays</h2>

<ul class="posts">
